                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3823" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0189</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9526 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">删繁就简三级变，新桃总把旧符迁——大数据背景下陕西移动运维管理业务流程再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Three Levels of Change to Simplify the Complex, Old Couplets are Replaced with New Ones——Shaanxi Mobile’s Business Process Reengineering of Operation and Maintenance Management in the Context of Big Data</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">楼旭明，刘立，陈子凤，成泷，高熙梅，侯昆丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国移动通信集团陕西有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西移动；战略管理；业务流程；流程再造；2019百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Shaanxi Mobile; Strategic Management; Business Process; Process Reengineering;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了陕西移动在国家、集团、省公司提出大数据战略要求，明确大数据正在从舆论炒作向产业落地发展的背景下，考虑到企业内外的诸多影响因素，为了更好的加速行业转型，以流程为载体，运用流程再造的相关理念构建多维开放数据价值链管理生态体系，积极优化公司网络运维管理体系，提高服务质量、运作能力以及客户满意度的故事。通过对本案例的学习，可以帮助学习者了解流程再造的理念和实施过程，引导学习者思考流程再造对企业转型升级的重要性。本案例旨在为企业顺应大数据时代的转型优化提供借鉴，同时也可以作为案例供本科生和研究生在学习中运用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the strategic requirements of big data put forward by the national, the group and the provincial company, Shaanxi mobile has considered many influence factors of inside and outside the enterprise, in order to accelerate the industry transition, in order to process as the carrier, apply the related concept of process reengineering build multi-dimensional open data value chain management of ecological system, optimize the company network operations management system actively, improve service quality, operation ability, and customer satisfaction. Through the study of this case, we can help learners to understand the idea and implementation process of reengineering, and guide learners to think about the importance of reengineering for enterprise transformation and upgrading. The purpose of this case is to provide reference for enterprises to adapt to the transformation and optimization of big data era, and also can be used as a case for undergraduates and postgraduates in their study.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《现代企业管理》、《流程再造》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SWOT 分析 业务流程 流程再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-07</td>
                            </tr>
